  quest_name: It's Dangerous to Go Alone
  description: 'Since you''re just startin'' your adventure, you''ll need something
    to begin with. I bought a sword off some weird fella - looked half mad, but the
    blade was decent. Wait, where''d i put it. Agh right, forgot it at Joe''s. Go
    talk to the blacksmith - he''s holdin'' onto weapon worthy of a hero like you. '
